{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_013NKvdwKeNDfZnauu3wShrs","type":"tool_result","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Perfect! I've successfully read all the E2E helper files and configuration. Here's a comprehensive summary of the established patterns and dependencies:\n\n## Import Patterns and Coding Style\n\n### Wallet Helpers (`wallets.ts`)\n- **Imports**: `@solana/web3.js` (Connection, Keypair, PublicKey, LAMPORTS_PER_SOL)\n- **Pattern**: Deterministic keypairs using fixed seed bytes for reproducibility\n- **Constants**: `PLAYER_A`, `PLAYER_B` (exported), `LOCAL_RPC_URL`, `DEFAULT_AIRDROP_SOL`\n- **Key Functions**:\n  - `fundWallet(connection, to, solAmount?)` — single wallet airdrop + confirmation\n  - `fundTestWallets(rpcUrl?, solAmount?)` — returns `{ playerA, playerB, connection }` with validation\n- **Style**: JSDoc comments, promise-based, validation with error messages\n\n### Page Objects (`page-objects.ts`)\n- **Imports**: `@playwright/test` (Page, Locator, expect)\n- **Pattern**: CSS-class-based selectors, constant `sel` object with nested structure, TypeScript types\n- **Type Definitions**: `CoinSide` (\"heads\" | \"tails\"), `Tier` (6 values), exported types\n- **Helper Functions Structure**:\n  - Navigation: `navigateToCoinflip(page)`, `waitForLobby(page, timeout?)`\n  - Interactions: `selectTier(page, tier)`, `selectSide(page, side)`, `createMatch()`, `joinMatch()`, `cancelMatch()`, `claimOrSettle()`, `backToLobby()`\n  - Wait/Assert primitives: `waitForPhaseLabel()`, `waitForResult()`, `waitForLobbyMatch()`, `assertLobbyEmpty()`, `assertErrorToast()`, `assertNoErrorToast()`, `waitForText()`\n  - Utilities: `getSolBalance(page, walletAddress, rpcUrl?)`, `trackConsoleErrors(page)` — returns `{ errors, assertClean }`\n- **Style**: JSDoc per function, async/await, optional parameters with defaults, `expect()` from Playwright\n\n### Smoke Test (`smoke.spec.ts`)\n- **Structure**: `test.describe(\"Local E2E smoke\", () => { test(\"name\", async ({ page }) => { ... }) })`\n- **Pattern**: Direct page navigation, selector via `.locator()`, assertions via `expect()`, console error tracking\n- **Minimal setup**: No helper imports needed, uses raw Playwright API\n\n### Config (`playwright.local.config.ts`)\n- **Pattern**: `defineConfig()` from Playwright, single project \"local-e2e\"\n- **Key Settings**: \n  - Test directory: `./e2e`, test match: `local/**/*.spec.ts`\n  - Workers: 1, retries: 0, timeout: 60s\n  - Base URL: `http://localhost:3002` (Vite dev server on port 3002)\n  - Web server starts with env vars: `VITE_MOCK_MODE=false`, `VITE_RPC_URL=http://127.0.0.1:8899`, `VITE_SOLANA_NETWORK=localnet`\n  - Trace retention: \"retain-on-failure\"\n\n## Available Dependencies\n\n### In `package.json`:\n- **Runtime**: \n  - `@coral-xyz/anchor` (v0.32.1)\n  - `@solana/web3.js` (v1.98.0)\n  - `@rng-utopia/*` workspace packages (anchor-client, game-engine, ui, wallet, config)\n  - React 18.3, React Router 7.1\n  \n- **Dev**: \n  - `@playwright/test` (v1.58.2)\n  - `typescript` (v5.7.0)\n  - `vite` (v6.0.0)\n  - `eslint`\n\n## Key Takeaways\n\n1. **CSS-based selectors** throughout (not data-test attributes) — target `.coinflip-*` and `.rng-*` classes\n2. **Timeout patterns**: 5s for quick UI, 10-15s for network, 30s for phase waits\n3. **Assertions use `expect()` from Playwright** with custom matchers like `.toHaveClass()`, `.toContainText()`, `.toHaveCount()`\n4. **RPC calls via `page.evaluate()`** for in-browser JSON-RPC to local validator\n5. **No mocking in local tests** — real Solana RPC, real wallets, real transactions\n6. **Error tracking** via `page.on(\"console\", ...)` filter for non-critical browser noise\n7. **JSDoc style** used consistently for all exported functions\n8. **TypeScript throughout** — strict typing for Tier, CoinSide, Page locators"},{"type":"text","text":"agentId: ab92e8e0abe723dfe (for resuming to continue this agent's work if needed)\n<usage>total_tokens: 35633\ntool_uses: 5\nduration_ms: 15915</usage>"}]}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"5c7393b1-80a9-4d3b-9693-3efb14711fd2","uuid":"44fb41dc-7de7-4a82-91d3-b56f5eccd281","tool_use_result":{"status":"completed","prompt":"Read the existing E2E helper files to understand the patterns and imports already established:\n\n1. `sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/e2e/local/helpers/wallets.ts` - wallet helpers\n2. `sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/e2e/local/helpers/page-objects.ts` - page object helpers\n3. `sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/e2e/local/smoke.spec.ts` - existing smoke test\n4. `sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/playwright.local.config.ts` - local config\n\nAlso check what dependencies are available in `sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/package.json` (specifically @solana/web3.js, anchor, etc.)\n\nReturn the import patterns, coding style, and available dependencies.","agentId":"ab92e8e0abe723dfe","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Perfect! I've successfully read all the E2E helper files and configuration. Here's a comprehensive summary of the established patterns and dependencies:\n\n## Import Patterns and Coding Style\n\n### Wallet Helpers (`wallets.ts`)\n- **Imports**: `@solana/web3.js` (Connection, Keypair, PublicKey, LAMPORTS_PER_SOL)\n- **Pattern**: Deterministic keypairs using fixed seed bytes for reproducibility\n- **Constants**: `PLAYER_A`, `PLAYER_B` (exported), `LOCAL_RPC_URL`, `DEFAULT_AIRDROP_SOL`\n- **Key Functions**:\n  - `fundWallet(connection, to, solAmount?)` — single wallet airdrop + confirmation\n  - `fundTestWallets(rpcUrl?, solAmount?)` — returns `{ playerA, playerB, connection }` with validation\n- **Style**: JSDoc comments, promise-based, validation with error messages\n\n### Page Objects (`page-objects.ts`)\n- **Imports**: `@playwright/test` (Page, Locator, expect)\n- **Pattern**: CSS-class-based selectors, constant `sel` object with nested structure, TypeScript types\n- **Type Definitions**: `CoinSide` (\"heads\" | \"tails\"), `Tier` (6 values), exported types\n- **Helper Functions Structure**:\n  - Navigation: `navigateToCoinflip(page)`, `waitForLobby(page, timeout?)`\n  - Interactions: `selectTier(page, tier)`, `selectSide(page, side)`, `createMatch()`, `joinMatch()`, `cancelMatch()`, `claimOrSettle()`, `backToLobby()`\n  - Wait/Assert primitives: `waitForPhaseLabel()`, `waitForResult()`, `waitForLobbyMatch()`, `assertLobbyEmpty()`, `assertErrorToast()`, `assertNoErrorToast()`, `waitForText()`\n  - Utilities: `getSolBalance(page, walletAddress, rpcUrl?)`, `trackConsoleErrors(page)` — returns `{ errors, assertClean }`\n- **Style**: JSDoc per function, async/await, optional parameters with defaults, `expect()` from Playwright\n\n### Smoke Test (`smoke.spec.ts`)\n- **Structure**: `test.describe(\"Local E2E smoke\", () => { test(\"name\", async ({ page }) => { ... }) })`\n- **Pattern**: Direct page navigation, selector via `.locator()`, assertions via `expect()`, console error tracking\n- **Minimal setup**: No helper imports needed, uses raw Playwright API\n\n### Config (`playwright.local.config.ts`)\n- **Pattern**: `defineConfig()` from Playwright, single project \"local-e2e\"\n- **Key Settings**: \n  - Test directory: `./e2e`, test match: `local/**/*.spec.ts`\n  - Workers: 1, retries: 0, timeout: 60s\n  - Base URL: `http://localhost:3002` (Vite dev server on port 3002)\n  - Web server starts with env vars: `VITE_MOCK_MODE=false`, `VITE_RPC_URL=http://127.0.0.1:8899`, `VITE_SOLANA_NETWORK=localnet`\n  - Trace retention: \"retain-on-failure\"\n\n## Available Dependencies\n\n### In `package.json`:\n- **Runtime**: \n  - `@coral-xyz/anchor` (v0.32.1)\n  - `@solana/web3.js` (v1.98.0)\n  - `@rng-utopia/*` workspace packages (anchor-client, game-engine, ui, wallet, config)\n  - React 18.3, React Router 7.1\n  \n- **Dev**: \n  - `@playwright/test` (v1.58.2)\n  - `typescript` (v5.7.0)\n  - `vite` (v6.0.0)\n  - `eslint`\n\n## Key Takeaways\n\n1. **CSS-based selectors** throughout (not data-test attributes) — target `.coinflip-*` and `.rng-*` classes\n2. **Timeout patterns**: 5s for quick UI, 10-15s for network, 30s for phase waits\n3. **Assertions use `expect()` from Playwright** with custom matchers like `.toHaveClass()`, `.toContainText()`, `.toHaveCount()`\n4. **RPC calls via `page.evaluate()`** for in-browser JSON-RPC to local validator\n5. **No mocking in local tests** — real Solana RPC, real wallets, real transactions\n6. **Error tracking** via `page.on(\"console\", ...)` filter for non-critical browser noise\n7. **JSDoc style** used consistently for all exported functions\n8. **TypeScript throughout** — strict typing for Tier, CoinSide, Page locators"}],"totalDurationMs":15915,"totalTokens":35633,"totalToolUseCount":5,"usage":{"input_tokens":7,"cache_creation_input_tokens":9771,"cache_read_input_tokens":24657,"output_tokens":1198,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":9771,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"}}}
